  "claude_code_prompt": "Build the MVP for a web app called Deckmetry. Deckmetry will initially launch only for Wehrung's as a supplier-side validation pilot. Do not build a multi-supplier marketplace yet, but structure the database with supplier_id fields so multi-supplier support can be added later. The app needs two main dashboards: Supplier Dashboard and Contractor Dashboard. Supplier Dashboard menu: Contractors, Homeowners / Leads, Catalog, Reports. Contractor Dashboard menu: Projects, New Project, Orders / History, Account. Build the MVP according to the structured requirements in this JSON file. Keep the UI clean, professional, and simple. The platform should feel practical for salespeople and contractors, not like a complicated enterprise system. This is a validation MVP for Wehrung's, so the goal is speed, clarity, and usefulness."
}